    <article class="prose">
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>

      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> February 11, 2026</p>

      <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing or using {SITE_NAME}, you agree to these Terms of Use. If you don't agree,
        please don't use the site.
