        We are not a government agency, and our articles are not official government communications.
      </p>
      <p>
        We transform publicly available government data into readable articles. Every article
        links to its original source. <strong>When in doubt, the official government source
        is always authoritative.</strong>
      </p>

      <h2>Not Professional Advice</h2>
      <p>
        {SITE_NAME} does not provide:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Legal advice or guidance</li>
        <li>Medical or health advice</li>
        <li>Financial or investment advice</li>
        <li>Professional consulting of any kind</li>
      </ul>
